public class RenderEngine2D
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.event.MouseMotionListener, java.awt.event.MouseListener, java.awt.event.KeyListener

The RenderEngine2D class provides all methods that are required for drawing to an OpenGL canvas. This includes method to initialize rendering, handle resizes of the canvas and to render a single frame.
